187
00:12:42,145 --> 00:12:46,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, aku merasa pernah melihatnya.</font>

188
00:12:47,784 --> 00:12:49,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kenapa bisa kembali kesana?</font>

189
00:12:49,385 --> 00:12:52,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingat mengambil dompetnya.</font>

190
00:12:53,556 --> 00:12:55,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, jangan dipikirkan.</font>

191
00:12:55,191 --> 00:12:57,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Paling tidak, aku tidak tertangkap oleh detektif.</font>

192
00:12:59,829 --> 00:13:01,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi ini lucu.</font>

193
00:13:01,464 --> 00:13:04,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokgo Oppa tidak meneleponku lagi.</font>

194
00:13:04,901 --> 00:13:08,270
