206
00:13:47,176 --> 00:13:48,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menahanku.</font>

207
00:13:48,678 --> 00:13:50,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau...</font>

208
00:13:50,179 --> 00:13:52,440
<font color=#FFFF00>...meregangkan kakimu seperti itu...</font>

209
00:13:52,448 --> 00:13:55,780
<font color=#FFFF00>...di depan detektif?</font>

210
00:13:55,785 --> 00:13:58,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Wajar saja kalau dia menjadi gila
